<br>
There is a severe imbalance with casters vs melee now.  As more and more uber weapons entered the game the damage output of melee increased greatly while the casters stayed the same.  To make us viable in groups while maintaining the description of the class as it was meant to be we need increased mana regen or more efficient nukes.  This is a problem with all int casters, however, it is more apparent in wizards who are solely dependant on mana to be useful in a group.<br>
